data.description: Almost 20 acres irrigated new variety hazelnut orchard in Linn County. Chehalis Silt Clay Loam soil is an excellent soil for growing hazelnuts. Wepster/McDonald mix was planted in 2019. Water rights from a 65 GPM well with a 8" well and 7.5 HP pump. 30 x 50 shop with concrete floor and two roll up doors. Now is the time to jump on having that hazelnut orchard you have dreamed of.
